---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Conflict Resolution Workshops | Africa Peace Initiative">
  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
  <header class="header">
    <nav class="container navbar">
      <div class="logo">
        <a href="/">
          <img
            src="https://ik.imagekit.io/5zp8ovb7c/Africa%20Peace%20Initiative/API%20logo-12.png?updatedAt=1741074058148"
            alt="Africa Peace Initiative Logo"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
      <button
        class="hamburger"
        aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="nav-links"
      >
        <span class="bar"></span>
        <span class="bar"></span>
        <span class="bar"></span>
      </button>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#about">Who We Are</a></li>
        <li><a href="#programs">Our Approach</a></li>
        <li><a href="#get-involved">Get Involved</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="accent-line"></div>
  </header>
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const hamburger = document.querySelector(".hamburger");
      const navLinks = document.querySelector(".nav-links");
      if (!hamburger || !navLinks) {
        console.error("Error: Hamburger or navLinks element not found!");
        return;
      }
      hamburger.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const isExpanded = hamburger.getAttribute("aria-expanded") === "true";
        hamburger.setAttribute("aria-expanded", String(!isExpanded));
        navLinks.classList.toggle("active");
      });
    });
  </script>
  <section
    class="hero-banner"
    style="background: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?africa,peace') center/cover no-repeat; height: 500px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; color: white; background-blend-mode: overlay; background-color: rgba(19, 61, 25, 0.8); animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;"
  >
    <div
      class="hero-content container"
      style="animation: slideUp 1.2s ease-in-out;"
    >
      <h1
        class="hero-headline"
        style="font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); color: #e69a28;"
      >
        Empowering Peace Through Conflict Resolution Workshops
      </h1>
      <p
        class="hero-subheadline"
        style="font-size: 1.8rem; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); color: #eef5e9;"
      >
        Join us as we foster dialogue, understanding, and sustainable peace
        across African communities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    class="content-section"
    style="background-color: #eef5e9; padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center; color: #133d19;"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.8rem;">Our Conflict Resolution Workshops</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">
        At Africa Peace Initiative, we believe in the power of dialogue and
        collaboration to resolve conflicts and build lasting peace. Our
        workshops are designed to empower individuals and communities with the
        skills and tools needed to address disputes constructively and foster
        harmony.
      </p>
      
      <div
        style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: left; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"
      >
        <h3 style="font-size: 2rem;">A Vision for Lasting Peace</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.8;">
          At the heart of Africa Peace Initiative lies a vision where every
          community can live free from the shadows of conflict. Our workshops
          are not just about resolving disputes but also about nurturing
          resilience and fostering a culture of peace. By focusing on
          grassroots-level engagement, we aim to create a ripple effect that
          transforms entire regions. From post-conflict recovery programs to
          proactive peace education, our initiatives are tailored to meet the
          unique needs of each community we serve.
        </p>
        <h3 style="font-size: 2rem;">Empowering Local Champions</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.8;">
          One of the cornerstones of our approach is empowering local
          champions—individuals who are deeply rooted in their communities and
          committed to driving change. These champions undergo rigorous training
          in conflict analysis, mediation, and leadership. Equipped with these
          skills, they become catalysts for peace, bridging divides and
          inspiring others to follow suit. Through mentorship and ongoing
          support, we ensure that these leaders remain at the forefront of
          peacebuilding efforts long after our workshops conclude.
        </p>
        <h3 style="font-size: 2rem;">Building Bridges Across Borders</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.8;">
          Conflict often transcends borders, affecting entire regions and
          generations. At Africa Peace Initiative, we recognize the
          interconnected nature of peace and security. That’s why our workshops
          bring together participants from diverse backgrounds, cultures, and
          countries. By fostering cross-border dialogue and collaboration, we
          break down barriers and build bridges of understanding. This regional
          approach ensures that peacebuilding efforts are holistic, inclusive,
          and impactful, paving the way for a brighter future for all Africans.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    class="cta-section"
    style="background-color: #133d19; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px;"
  >
    <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Join Our Next Workshop</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.3rem;">
      Learn how you can participate in our upcoming conflict resolution
      workshops and contribute to peacebuilding efforts across Africa.
    </p>
    <a
      href="#"
      class="cta-button"
      style="display: inline-block; background: #e69a28; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.4rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; transition: background 0.3s ease;"
      >Register Now</a
    >
  </section>
  <footer id="contact">
    <div class="container footer-content">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <ul class="contact-info">
          <li>
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            <a href="mailto:info@africapeaceinitiative.org"
              >info@africapeaceinitiative.org</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
            <a href="tel:+19297612735">+1 (929) 761-2735</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> 12 Peace Street, Nairobi, Kenya
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>Follow Us</h3>
        <ul class="social-links">
          <li>
            <a href="https://facebook.com/api" aria-label="Facebook"
              ><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i> Facebook</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/api" aria-label="Twitter"
              ><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i> Twitter</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"
              ><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"
              ><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>Stay Updated</h3>
        <p>Subscribe to our newsletter for the latest news.</p>
        <form class="newsletter-form" action="/subscribe" method="POST">
          <input
            type="email"
            class="newsletter-input"
            placeholder="Enter your email"
            required
            aria-label="Newsletter email"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="cta-button primary-button"
            >Subscribe</button
          >
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom container">
      <p>
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} Africa Peace Initiative. All rights reserved.
        |
        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const hamburger = document.querySelector(".hamburger");
    const navLinks = document.querySelector(".nav-links");
    if (!hamburger || !navLinks) {
      console.error("Error: Hamburger or navLinks element not found!");
      return;
    }
    hamburger.addEventListener("click", () => {
      const isExpanded = hamburger.getAttribute("aria-expanded") === "true";
      hamburger.setAttribute("aria-expanded", String(!isExpanded));
      navLinks.classList.toggle("active");
    });
  });
</script>
<style lang="scss">
  @use "sass:color";
  /* Variables */
  :root {
    --primary-color: #2e8b57;
    --primary-darker: #226441;
    --secondary-color: #ffffff;
    --off-white: #f0fff0;
    --dark-green: #006400;
    --accent-color: #38761d;
    --blue-accent: #4682b4;
    --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    --spacing-unit: 24px;
    --border-radius: 8px;
    --neutral-light: #f2f2f2;
    --neutral-dark: #333333;
    --headline-font: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    --subheadline-font: "Roboto", sans-serif;
  }
  .header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  .container.navbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .logo img {
    height: 60px;
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }
  .logo img:hover {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.5)); /* Subtle green glow */
  }
  .hamburger {
    display: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hamburger .bar {
    display: block;
    width: 30px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #1a3c5e; /* Darker blue for contrast */
    margin: 6px 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] .bar:nth-child(1) {
    transform: translateY(9px) rotate(45deg);
  }
  .hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] .bar:nth-child(2) {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] .bar:nth-child(3) {
    transform: translateY(-9px) rotate(-45deg);
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .nav-links li {
    margin: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    color: #1a3c5e; /* Darker blue for better contrast */
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: "Arial", sans-serif; /* Replace with NGO’s font */
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    border-radius: 25px; /* Capsule shape */
  }
  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: #27ae60;
    background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.1); /* Light green bg on hover */
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .accent-line {
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      #0057b7,
      #27ae60
    ); /* Blue-to-green gradient */
    width: 100%;
  }
  /* Mobile Styles */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hamburger {
      display: block;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      background: #fff;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem 0;
      z-index: 999;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      transform: translateX(100%);
      box-shadow: -5px 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .nav-links.active {
      display: flex;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    .nav-links li {
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #1a3c5e;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: none; /* No hover bg on mobile */
    }
    .accent-line {
      display: none; /* Hide accent line on mobile */
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .logo img {
      height: 50px;
    }
    .hamburger {
      width: 35px;
      height: 35px;
    }
    .hamburger .bar {
      width: 25px;
      height: 2px;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
    .container.navbar {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(30px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #c48222;
  }
  /* Footer */
  footer {
    background: var(--neutral-dark);
    padding: 40px 0 20px;
    .footer-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .footer-col {
      h3 {
        color: var(--secondary-color);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        li {
          margin-bottom: 12px;
          a {
            color: var(--off-white);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            &:hover,
            &:focus {
              color: var(--primary-color);
              outline: none;
            }
          }
          i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
          }
        }
      }
      .newsletter-form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        .newsletter-input {
          padding: 10px;
          flex: 1;
          border: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          font-size: 1rem;
          &:focus {
            outline: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
          }
        }
        .cta-button {
          padding: 10px 20px;
          border: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          background: var(--primary-color);
          color: white;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 1rem;
          transition: background 0.3s ease;
          &:hover {
            background: var(--primary-darker);
          }
          &:focus {
            outline: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
          }
        }
      }
    }
    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--neutral-light);
      padding-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      p {
        color: var(--off-white);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      a {
        color: var(--off-white);
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
        &:hover,
        &:focus {
          color: var(--primary-color);
          outline: none;
        }
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .footer-content {
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .footer-col {
        h3 {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        ul li a {
          font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .newsletter-form {
          flex-direction: column;
          .newsletter-input {
            width: 100%;
          }
          .cta-button {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
          }
        }
      }
      .footer-bottom p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
